name: Ski Park Tycoon Maps and Mods
body: Click on view on GitHub to select which file you want to download, or you can just download this whole thing to get all of the maps and mods for Ski Park Tycoon. If you want to add files to this, message me on steam so I can add you as a collaborator.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
